  "text": "The immunohistochemical study ameloblastomas express cytokeratins 5/6, 13, 14, and 19. CK13 is preferentially expressed in the stellate reticulum like cells, CK14 in peripheral cells and CK19 in all cells. [CITATION_1] The lesion was excised entirely in a conservative approach. Our case completed two months of follow up with no signs of relapse.",
